Huanglong Scenic and Historic Interest Area in Songpan County in southwest China's Sichuan Province is a superlative natural property with forests, mountain scenery and a series of travertine lakes. Known for its rich biodiversity, the area is home to many beautiful and precious plants. Let's take a look at some of the beautiful and precious plants growing in Huanglong. (The video is provided by Sun Jiapeng and edited by Liu Haibo) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)